Matthew Smith Games - Enhanced Collection
========================================

This collection contains enhanced ports of classic ZX Spectrum games originally created by Matthew Smith.

ORIGINAL GAMES
==============

Manic Miner (1983)
- Original game © Matthew Smith
- Published by Bug-Byte Ltd. / Software Projects Ltd.

Jet Set Willy (1984) 
- Original game © Matthew Smith
- Published by Software Projects Ltd.

