DISCLAIMER
==========

This collection is created for educational, historical preservation, and 
entertainment purposes. The original games remain the intellectual property 
of Matthew Smith and their respective publishers.

The enhanced ports maintain 100% identical gameplay to the originals while
adding modern compatibility features.

No commercial use is intended or implied. This is a community preservation
project celebrating classic gaming history.
